text: Parvanachis is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==Species== Species within the genus Parvanachis include: * Parvanachis obesa (C. B. Adams, 1845) * Parvanachis ostreicola (Sowerby III, 1882) ==References== Category:Columbellidae
title: Parvanachis
